  cardName: "Li\xEAn Qu\xE2n Th\u1ECBnh Y\u1EBFn"
  cardImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 23c8c2c7108baa249a286044e4c52e40, type: 3}
  cardDescription: "Giai \u0111o\u1EA1n h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng, b\u1EA1n s\u1EED
    d\u1EE5ng l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y l\xEAn b\u1EA3n th\xE2n v\xE0 t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i thu\u1ED9c 1 th\u1EBF l\u1EF1c kh\xE1c \u0111\xE3 x\xE1c
    \u0111\u1ECBnh th\u1EBF l\u1EF1c do b\u1EA1n ch\u1ECDn.\r\nB\u1EA1n ch\u1ECDn
    1 h\u1EA1ng m\u1EE5c:\r\nB\u1EA1n h\u1ED3i ph\u1EE5c X \u0111i\u1EC3m sinh l\u1EF1c.\r\nB\u1EA1n
    r\xFAt X l\xE1 b\xE0i.\r\n(X l\xE0 s\u1ED1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i ch\u01A1i
    c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a th\u1EBF l\u1EF1c m\xE0 b\u1EA1n ch\u1ECDn).\r\n\r\nSau
    \u0111\xF3 m\u1ED7i m\u1EE5c ti\xEAu kh\xE1c b\u1EA1n r\xFAt 1 l\xE1 b\xE0i v\xE0
    tho\xE1t kh\u1ECFi tr\u1EA1ng th\xE1i Li\xEAn ho\xE0n."
